            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CodexMate 0.0.11

- Fixed a menu status bug where the pixel character could keep showing Running when no visible thread was actually running.
- Kept background active-turn detection available for thread backfill without letting stale hints override the displayed menu status.
- Added regression coverage for unattributed active-turn hints so the menu status stays aligned with the visible thread list.
]]></description>
